#### Secondary Colors

Supporting colors for variety.

#### Semantic Colors

Colors with specific meanings:

| Color | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| Success | Positive outcomes, confirmations |
| Warning | Cautions, attention needed |
| Error | Problems, failures |
| Info | Neutral information |

#### Color Guidelines

- Maintain contrast ratios (WCAG AA: 4.5:1)
- Don't use too many colors together
- Be consistent across touchpoints
- Document when/where to use each color

### Typography

#### Font Selection

Choose fonts that:
- Are readable at all sizes
- Support needed languages
- Have enough weights
- Match brand personality
- Load performantly

